<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
  	<div class="pull_HN_page" style="margin-top:40px;">
	   	<h1 style="font-size:30px;text-align:center;margin-bottom:25px;margin-top:53px;">Hello! These are the statistics figures and most interesting stories currently in Hacker news</h1>
		<div class="figures">
			<h3>These are the statistics scores for the set of stories currently in the Hacker News front page</h3>
			<div style="background: lime;float: left;width: 250px;text-align: center;font-size: 20px;font-weight: bold;margin-bottom: 10px;height: 30px;padding-top: 7px;">Mean: <%= sprintf("%.2f", @mean_value) %></div>
			<div style="background: lime;float: left;width: 250px;text-align: center;font-size: 20px;font-weight: bold;margin-bottom: 10px;height: 30px;padding-top: 7px;">Median: <%= @median_value %></div>
			<div style="background: lime;float: left;width: 250px;text-align: center;font-size: 20px;font-weight: bold;margin-bottom: 10px;height: 30px;padding-top: 7px;">Mode: <%= @mode_value %></div>
		</div>
		<h3> And below you can find the most interesting stories, with more points than the median</h3>
		<table style="background: #A8A8A8;margin-bottom:20px;">
		  <tr style=" border: 2px solid #fafafa;font-size:13px;color:white;background: #383838;">
		    <th>Title</th>
		    <th>URL</th>
		    <th>Hacker News Id</th>
		    <th>Number of comments</th>
		    <th>Points</th>
		    <th>Posted ago</th>
		    <th>Posted By</th>
		  </tr>
		 
		<% @items_to_send.each do |item| %>
		  <tr style=" border: 2px solid #fafafa; background: #6D9;font-weight:bold;">		
			    <td style="text-align:center;"><%= item["title"] %></td>
			    <td style="text-align:center;"><%= item["url"] %></td>
			    <td style="text-align:center;"><%= item["id"] %></td>
			    <td style="text-align:center;"><%= item["commentCount"] %></td>
			    <td style="font-size:18px;style="text-align:center;""><%= item["points"] %></td>
			    <td style="text-align:center;"><%= item["postedAgo"] %></td>
			    <td style="text-align:center;"><%= item["postedBy"] %></td>
		  </tr>
		<% end %>
		</table>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>